Badwolf 1.4.0 - 2025-08-14

== Highlights ==
- Ctrl-Escape can now be used to terminate the web process used by the current tab
- Command line options -i disables images, and -S enables JavaScript
- New Translation: Serbian

== Full Changelog ==

